The Telegraph - Calcutta : International
 Sunday, August 01, 2004 				 Cage weds again, this time waitress
				 	 Nicolas Cage: Third-time lucky?Los Angeles, July 31 (AFP): Oscar-winning US actor Nicolas Cage has married his former Sushi waitress girlfriend, Alice Kim, just two months after finalising his divorce from Lisa Marie Presley, reports say.																								The Hollywood star tied the knot with the 20-year-old Korean-American, who he met five months ago when she served him in a Los Angeles restaurant, at a private ceremony in northern California yesterday, the entertainment press said.																								E-online and other industry publications quoted Cages spokeswoman as confirming the marriage  Cages third union and Kims first  took place on a ranch far from the spotlights of Hollywood.																								Cages ill-fated marriage to Elvis Presleys daughter finally ended in May after their romantic August 2002 wedding in Hawaii. 																								The 40-year-old actor, the nephew of legendary filmmaker Francis Ford Coppola who won the best actor Oscar for 1995s Leaving Las Vegas, was also married to actress Patricia Arquette from 1995 to 2001.
